data.description: This impeccably crafted 3 bed/2 bath brick & stone home in Spring Creek offers refined living. Featuring vinyl plank & tile floors, crown molding, and high ceilings, it exudes elegance. The kitchen boasts granite counters and stainless appliances, flowing into a spacious living area with a gas fireplace. The master suite impresses with a tray ceiling, dual walk-in closets, and a luxurious bath. Outside, a fenced yard with a covered patio, gas grill hookup, and sprinkler system beckons outdoor enjoyment.
